      <title>俄罗斯计划在炼油厂遭受最近袭击后采取反无人机应对措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/russia-plans-anti-drone-response-after-recent-hits-on-refineries</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在无人机多次袭击乌克兰邻近地区以及对距离边境较远的目标（特别是炼油厂）进行袭击后，俄罗斯正在加强对抗无人机的军事训练。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/russia-plans-anti-drone-response-after-recent-hits-on-refineries</guid>
